high_descs: turn and walk to the stove
pick up the knife that is on the counter next to the stove
turn and walk  to the  tall brown Shelf
take the glass cup off of the Shelf
Put The Knife into the glass cup
turn  and  walk to the sink
put the cup with the knife in it next to the sink
anns.task_desc: Put The Knife  into a cup  and  put it next to the sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk around the island. Go to the counter next to the oven and turn left to face it.
Pick up the knife off of the counter.
Turn to the left and go forward then turn to the right to face the brown shelves.
Place the knife inside the bowl.
pick up the bowl and knife from the shelves.
Turn to the left then go straight to the counter by the sink.
Place the bowl and knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and knife to a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the wooden shelves and turn left at the sink to face the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the knife in front of the head of lettuce on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the wooden shelves on the right.
Put the knife inside the clear glass on the top shelf of the wooden rack.
Pick up the clear glass with the knife inside from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the glass with the knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a knife in a sink.
